### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/transactions/v1
@apiKey = dev-api-key-change-me
@importId = c68d97fa-da70-44ec-830a-4daf7cbed516

### ─── IMPORTS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Upload CSV file
# @name uploadCsv
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="transactions.csv"
Content-Type: text/plain

iban,date,amount,currency,category,description
DE89370400440532013000,2024-03-15,100.50,EUR,groceries,Supermarket
DE89370400440532013000,2024-03-16,-45.00,EUR,transport,Bus ticket
GB29NWBK60161331926819,2024-03-10,200.00,GBP,transport,Train ticket
DE89370400440532013000,2024-04-05,75.00,EUR,entertainment,Cinema
GB29NWBK60161331926819,2024-04-12,-30.00,GBP,groceries,Corner shop
--boundary--

###

### Get import status (uses importId captured from uploadCsv)
GET {{baseUrl}}/imports/{{importId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Get import status – explicit ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/imports/{{importId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Retry a failed import
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports/{{importId}}/retry
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Retry – explicit ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports/{{importId}}/retry
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Upload 100 records
# @name uploadCsv100
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="transactions-100.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./test-data/transactions-100.csv
--boundary--

###

### Upload 500 records
# @name uploadCsv500
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="transactions-500.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./test-data/transactions-500.csv
--boundary--

###

### Upload 10 000 records (performance / stress test)
# @name uploadCsv10000
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="transactions-10000.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./test-data/transactions-10000.csv
--boundary--

###

### Upload without API key → 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.csv"
Content-Type: text/plain

iban,date,amount,currency,category,description
DE89370400440532013000,2024-03-15,100.50,EUR,groceries,Test
--boundary--

### ─── STATISTICS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### All statistics (default page: page=0, size=20)
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Filter by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics?category=groceries
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Filter by IBAN
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics?iban=DE89370400440532013000
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Filter by month
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics?month=2024-03
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Filter by category + IBAN combined
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics?category=groceries&iban=DE89370400440532013000
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Filter by IBAN + month combined
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics?iban=GB29NWBK60161331926819&month=2024-04
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Pagination – page 0, size 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics?page=0&size=1
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Pagination – page 1, size 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics?page=1&size=1
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Pagination – large page size
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics?page=0&size=100
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### All filters combined with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics?category=groceries&iban=DE89370400440532013000&month=2024-03&page=0&size=5
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Statistics without API key → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics

### ─── HEALTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check (no auth required)
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

###
